{"tid":1460203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張達明：質疑警隊高層容許大批警員不展示委任證","createTime":"2019-08-13T01:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:36:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0dbaeeecd4375633dbfd684a0008a55ceceb31","tid":1460203,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:49:07.000Z","msg":"監警會前委員、港大法律學院首席講師張達明表示，相信監警會要跟進警隊在反修例事件的問題，會有非常大的困難。他說過往沒展示委任證的情況，涉及很小規模的行動，容易找出執法小隊，但現時是大規模，警員身上沒有辨識又戴上頭盔，相信很難找出涉事者。<br />\n<br />\n張達明在本台節目《千禧年代》質疑警隊高層容許前線違反通例，警員因為身分無法辨識而不受有效制約，對法治和警隊公信力破壞無可挽救，直言感到痛心，很難像以往一樣，認為香港警隊整體是優秀一流。<br />\n<br />\n張達明又說，近日看到警務人員廣泛地不跟從法律做事，例如即使警員在有足夠空間可先知會當事人涉嫌犯法下，卻一走近事主就即拘捕或用警棍毆打，無法分清對方是否犯事，無差別使用武力。"},{"pid":"6e00f7a79d564c251b00d3c8d194e7bc21f05723","tid":1460203,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:49:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474326-20190813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474326-20190813.htm&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9xzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=23d0524f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474326-20190813.htm&h=8719f059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474326-20190813.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7f5301c8a67583dacbe05981fa0399be4e574cb5","tid":1460203,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:51:26.000Z","msg":"今日先講委任證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又室內放煙又爆眼又公安你先講委任證"},{"pid":"3dc78024509a5a6d7f443e68e785c5d431ba938b","tid":1460203,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:36:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BeiA2k3NVd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBeiA2k3NV